(Philip): It depends, of course, on the vendor and their offerings. Many organizations are going partial T1, T1, T3, OC3 or other offerings at varying costs

(You): thanks. I'm trying to get a ballpark w/ the thought that SDSL and cable modems should've brought the price of T1s way down.



